 *  Struct data names changed from v2.x.x to v3.x.x
 *  ////////////////////////////////////////////////
 *
 * "ESP_Mail_Session" changes to "Session_Config"
 * "IMAP_Config" changes to "IMAP_Data"
 *
 * Changes in the examples
 *
 * ESP_Mail_Session session;
 * to
 * Session_Config config;
 *
 * IMAP_Config config;
 * to
 * IMAP_Data imap_data;
 *
